videos.headline: Oregon State RB breaks for 34-yard run, sets up TD
videos.description: Oregon State RB Artavis Pierce breaks loose for a 34-yard run, setting up a touchdown two plays later.

videos.headline: Oregon State RB finishes run with unreal juke for 62-yard TD
videos.description: Oregon State RB Jermar Jefferson breaks loose then finishes with a juke move, leaving two defenders on the ground.
